-- Tata Names Five-Person Panel to Search for Chairman Ratan Tata's Successor
-- Stephen Foxwell
-- 2010-08-06T13:02:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/tata-names-five-person-panel-to-search-for-chairman-ratan-tata-s-successor.html

          
          
             Tata group named a five-person panel
to search for the successor to Chairman Ratan Tata, according to
a statement today.  
 Tata Sons Ltd. Vice Chairman N.A. Soonawala, group directors
R.K. Krishnakumar and Cyrus Mistry, will be on the panel. Shirin
Bharucha and Lord Bhattacharya will also help select the new
head of the Mumbai-based group.  
          
          


  


        